OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe odd shower possible around
OL,6,Fthe east coast at first, but soon
OL,7,Fclearing east in the morning.
OL,8,FOtherwise cooler, dull and cloudy with
OL,9,Fsome patchy light drizzle possible.
OL,10,FBrightening up in the west in the
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FSome bright spells possible
OL,14,Fin the west at first. Otherwise dull
OL,15,Fand cloudy through the evening and
OL,16,Fovernight with perhaps some patchy
OL,17,Flight drizzle in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
