OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA dull and cloudy start then
OL,6,Fbrightening up for all through the day
OL,7,Fwith sunny intervals developing. A bit
OL,8,Fwarmer than Saturday.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,11,Fto Wednesday will be dry with sunny
OL,12,Fspells and becoming warmer inland,
OL,13,Fcooler and cloudier at times along
OL,14,Fimmediate coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
